    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Trademarked general term for daylight fluorescent and glow-in-the-dark paints and pigments, including objects colored by the pigments. Originally used only for products manufactured by Day-Glo Color Corporation, Cleveland, although the term is commonly used generally for flourescent pigments.</Note_Text>
